{% from "components/malta-national-identification-number-view/macro.njk" import maltaNationalIdentificationNumberView %}

<h2>Default</h2>
<dl>
  <dt>Malta National Identification Number</dt>
  <dd>{{ maltaNationalIdentificationNumberView({ value: "sample-value", label: "Malta National Identification Number" }) }}</dd>
</dl>

<h2>Format</h2>
<p>8 characters: 7 digits and a letter (A, B, G, H, L, M, P, or Z) that encodes geographic origin and registration era.</p>

<h2>Reference</h2>
<p>See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_identification_number#Malta">Malta National Identification Number</a>.</p>
